					"“Ah, I think I get it. I wouldn’t be able to use both hands, so it wouldn’t put any strain on my left shoulder...!”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“原来如此，看着打啊，确实这么一来用不上双手，就不会给左手负担了……！”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
